{
    "id": "aquaria/walstad",
    "title": "Set up a Walstad tank",
    "description": "Build a low-tech planted tank with staged setup proof, cycle monitoring, and a recovery loop before livestock.",
    "image": "/assets/quests/walstad_setup.jpg",
    "npc": "/assets/npc/vega.jpg",
    "start": "start",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "id": "start",
            "text": "Vega here. Walstad systems reward patience: stage clean materials, build layered substrate, then verify stability before any livestock move.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "stage",
                    "text": "Bench is clear and all components are ready.",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "83fe7eee-135e-4885-9ce0-9042b9fb860a",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "98609b23-4811-4275-8d83-ad59a2797753",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "75cec98f-fcf0-4d73-8d31-5a53571317b2",
                            "count": 3
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "62757412-be94-48c0-a1c0-8fad9bdb8c4a",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "0704e829-ce72-4c7d-91b0-8a774b11575d",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "c5a7574e-515f-4e9a-83fc-350703131f25",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "0564d441-7367-412e-b709-dad770814a39",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "16eb261b-9d93-4aff-ab31-40f6a78d04f1",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "stage",
            "text": "Condition fill water first so chlorine never touches plant roots. Keep all outlets above splash lines before you start pouring.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "condition-bucket-water",
                    "text": "Condition the bucket of replacement water."
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "build",
                    "text": "Dechlorinated water and tools are staged.",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "71efa72a-8c87-4dc2-8e2c-9119bb28fe50",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "build",
            "text": "Layer soil and gravel carefully, plant densely, then fill gently to avoid disturbing the cap. This build step is your first hard evidence gate.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "assemble-walstad-tank",
                    "text": "Assemble and plant the Walstad tank."
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "cycle-check",
                    "text": "Build artifact complete: planted Walstad tank is assembled.",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "785fa6f3-bb66-4197-a43f-52fea9cebd48",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "cycle-check",
            "text": "Now confirm early stability: run a first-day temperature check and inspect for sulfur smell, uprooted stems, or cloudy water before moving on.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "log-walstad-temperature",
                    "text": "Log a stabilization reading for the new setup."
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "interpret",
                    "text": "Reading and observation note are recorded.",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "785fa6f3-bb66-4197-a43f-52fea9cebd48",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "7f9d9d21-a4f2-4c48-b0e5-9a7483ab05d2",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "interpret",
            "text": "Pass if plants stay seated and temperature remains 24-28°C. If water turns cloudy or smells anaerobic, branch to recovery and re-check before closure.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "finish",
                    "text": "Stability checks passed; tank can continue cycling.",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "7f9d9d21-a4f2-4c48-b0e5-9a7483ab05d2",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "recover",
                    "text": "Clouding, odor, or temperature drift detected; start recovery loop.",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "785fa6f3-bb66-4197-a43f-52fea9cebd48",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "recover",
            "text": "Pause stocking plans. Remove decaying plant matter, shorten photoperiod, and keep equipment unplugged while hands are in the tank area; then retake measurements.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "log-walstad-temperature",
                    "text": "Capture a post-recovery stabilization reading."
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "interpret",
                    "text": "Recovery actions complete; review a fresh reading.",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "7f9d9d21-a4f2-4c48-b0e5-9a7483ab05d2",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "finish",
            "text": "Excellent. You now have setup proof and a stability check trail, so follow-on fish quests start from a safer baseline.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "finish",
                    "text": "Walstad base established."
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
